Our Story

Zanethemba Cleaning Services (Pty) Ltd was founded with a singular conviction: that cleanliness is an expression of hope. Our name, drawn from the Zulu word meaning "we bring hope," is not merely a brand identity — it is a lived commitment shaping every service we deliver.

We operate at the intersection of professional excellence and community upliftment, providing comprehensive cleaning, hygiene, and facility solutions across Gauteng. Our team is uniformed, trained, supervised, and deeply invested in the outcomes they create.

What sets us apart is our belief that a truly clean environment changes how people feel, work, and live. We have witnessed this transformation in offices we maintain, homes we restore, and industrial facilities we deep-clean.

As a proudly South African, community-rooted business, we are committed to creating dignified employment, investing in our people, and delivering services that don't merely meet expectations — they exceed them.

"We believe cleanliness promotes health, dignity and productivity — while uplifting the communities we serve."

Our Mission
To provide professional, efficient and affordable cleaning services that enhance well-being and bring hope through cleanliness.
Our Vision
To become a leading and trusted cleaning services provider in South Africa, recognised for excellence, integrity, and lasting community impact.
